    m_Localized: Oh, [wave]hello[/wave] there!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24304735268914
    m_Localized: 'Pirate: And only because you were once a pirate!'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24304735268913
    m_Localized: 'Pirate: But only this once.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24304735268912
    m_Localized: 'Pirate: Arr! I''ll let you go.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24304735268911
    m_Localized: 'Pirate: Yarr, you escaped me this time!'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24304735268910
    m_Localized: 'Narrator: You run...'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24304735268909
    m_Localized: 'Player: Oh no, I was robbed!'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24304735268908
    m_Localized: 'Pirate: Yeh understand? Just a one-time thing.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24304735268907
    m_Localized: 'Pirate: On account of yeh be an old crewmate.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24304735268906
    m_Localized: 'Pirate: Gimme half your money!'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24304735268905
    m_Localized: 'Pirate: All the space money! Now!'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24304735268904
    m_Localized: 'Pirate: I''ll take all your money! Yarr!'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24304735268903
    m_Localized: Ignore them.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24304735268902
    m_Localized: Hand over your (space) money.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24304735268901
    m_Localized: 'Player: Oh no! A space pirate!'
